Class SimpleArrayList<E>

java.lang.Object
  SimpleArrayList<E>

public class SimpleArrayList<E>
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides a simple generic list implemented as an array. It is similar to the ArrayList class included in the java.util package. The first element of the list is at position 0 and the last element is at position list.size() - 1. Except for the method next(), implementation of the SimpleArrayListIterator methods is left as part of your project.
